It's fantastic.

00:24:58.030 --> 00:25:01.720
And it's a great revelation to
see that all our lives, we've

00:25:01.720 --> 00:25:04.820
been saying I and me, but
when the attention turns back

00:25:04.820 --> 00:25:08.120
to that which is
our true nature,

00:25:08.120 --> 00:25:10.960
it's never been
touched yet by thought.

00:25:10.960 --> 00:25:13.050
It's beyond the
realm of everything

00:25:13.050 --> 00:25:14.720
that's been thought about.

00:25:14.720 --> 00:25:15.940
It's fresh.

00:25:15.940 --> 00:25:18.010
It's an undiscovered territory.

