It's a brilliantly innocent
and wise statement.

00:25:22.700 --> 00:25:25.020
I have no idea.

00:25:25.020 --> 00:25:26.670
I found out about
all this other stuff.

00:25:26.670 --> 00:25:29.720
I didn't actually check
out who I am, yeah.

