OK.

00:25:32.869 --> 00:25:36.520
So when we tune in to
this which is aware,

00:25:36.520 --> 00:25:39.760
it's a dimension of ourselves
which is naturally present.

00:25:39.760 --> 00:25:41.850
Thought is not so
naturally present.

00:25:41.850 --> 00:25:44.035
It's running in all directions.

00:25:44.035 --> 00:25:47.480
Reactive feeling is
not naturally present.

00:25:47.480 --> 00:25:48.990
But when you return
the attention

00:25:48.990 --> 00:25:52.610
to your own true nature,
it's naturally present.

00:25:52.610 --> 00:25:56.230
Presence without having
to try to be present.

00:25:56.230 --> 00:25:57.830
Anybody else like to contribute?

00:25:57.830 --> 00:25:58.626
Yeah.

00:25:58.626 --> 00:25:59.580
AUDIENCE: Nothing.

