Yeah.

00:26:03.400 --> 00:26:04.910
It's not a thing.

00:26:04.910 --> 00:26:08.820
That's also a brilliant,
amazing revelation to see.

00:26:08.820 --> 00:26:11.640
I've often referred
to myself as though I

00:26:11.640 --> 00:26:15.130
am a thing, as though
