But what's the difference
between no thing and no thing?

00:27:00.170 --> 00:27:04.280
It starts to dissolve the
trance of separation which

00:27:04.280 --> 00:27:08.540
we have lived in, most
of us our whole lives.

00:27:08.540 --> 00:27:11.990
The answers that other people
give to this kind of inquiry,

00:27:11.990 --> 00:27:15.200
and I've investigated this
with thousands and thousands,

00:27:15.200 --> 00:27:18.870
tens of thousands of people
over the last two decades,

00:27:18.870 --> 00:27:24.150
people will say things like
it's incredibly peaceful.

00:27:24.150 --> 00:27:25.920
There are no boundaries.

00:27:25.920 --> 00:27:30.010
There's no limits when I check
into this which I truly am,

00:27:30.010 --> 00:27:33.390
there's no beginning,
no end to it.

00:27:33.390 --> 00:27:35.710
It has no birth in time.

00:27:35.710 --> 00:27:39.100
It wasn't born, because
it's not a thing.

00:27:39.100 --> 00:27:41.030
And therefore it
also, it couldn't die.

