This ability to drop
into limitless dimension

00:28:20.330 --> 00:28:22.910
of yourself, limitless
consciousness, to have

00:28:22.910 --> 00:28:26.710
direct experiential recognition
of the dimension of yourself

00:28:26.710 --> 00:28:30.710
which is free, which was never
