00:47:32.760 --> 00:47:36.000
A new car is more of a desire.

00:47:36.000 --> 00:47:38.550
Whereas-- but
excitement and travel

00:47:38.550 --> 00:47:40.600
could be more of a
longing, you see.

00:47:40.600 --> 00:47:45.210
So a coach would help
you get clear about what

00:47:45.210 --> 00:47:46.430
